snippet.title: Christina Taft
snippet.description:
Welcome! Entrepreneur, egalitarian, futurist ✈️ Founder of Worldie.com - Social Media for Good. Create your own lane! Motivationology🐆

I work on making differences & changing paradigms. We create Technology for GOOD with partners & Worldie for equality, rescue, safety, integration, humanitarianism, progress internationally to improve & save lives. Safe & Equal World.
🌍To New Eras!

Tess Mercer/Lena Luthor (Smallville) is an Emulation Fav. She's CEO, Head of Daily Planet News, Tycoon, ambitious, passionate, resilient, overcomes adversity🧡 genius to build Better Worlds♟️
Love Wonder Woman/Diana Prince, Smart City Utopia matriarchy culture🧬

Fav Rock Music: Avril Lavigne, Carrie Underwood, Britney Spears, Kelly C
Fav Shows: Smallville, Wonder Woman, Sarah Walker (Chuck). Clark Kent, Oliver Queen, Joy
Amber Heard & United Nations SDG 5 are great!🚒
Enjoy heroics/cheerful scenes & inspiring leaders

I love shows, movies, scenes, music videos. I stand for causes, humanitarians, individuals🏖️
